Class CRCLCommandWrapper

  • java.lang.Object

            • crcl.utils.CRCLCommandWrapper

  • public class CRCLCommandWrapper
extends crcl.base.MessageType
    Command to be stored temporarily in the in memory CRCL program with additional associated actions wrapping another command.
    Author:
    Will Shackleford <william.shackleford@nist.gov>,<wshackle@gmail.com>
